node.text:
Hey guys it’s Jack & Lauren the creators of @doyoutravelpresets we have put together our first mobile tutorial on editing a sunset picture, to help you guys learn some new skills so you can get that perfect instagram photo! 
We want to share more tutorials with you all so please leave a comment and let us know what you thought and what you would like to see next!
You can shop our presets here www.doyoutravelpresets.com ❤️ #GypseaLust #doyoutravelXgypsealust #Presets #LRmobile #Tutorial

node.title: How to edit sunsets on mobile with Gypsea Lust
